    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Literary device in which a painting, sculpture, or other work of visual art is described in detail; the work may be real or imaginary. In original usage, was undertaken as a rhetorical exercise.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
